            <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-4">
                The investment thesis is clear: an opportunity to buy a world-class industry leader at a significant discount. The market is focused on near-term risks, potentially undervaluing UNH's long-term earnings power, robust cash flow, and shareholder-friendly policies. This is an investment for patient, risk-tolerant investors who believe the company's fundamental strengths will ultimately outweigh its current challenges.
